{"tid":2194681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12港人遭支那扣留仍未與外界接觸 代理律師被要求終止代理案件、被約談及受網絡攻擊","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T16:12:40.000Z","uid":124630,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49fee0d01bd131acc4060bbc5caf115126a380f0","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】在深圳關押中的12個被指偷渡的香港人，部分代理的律師被當局要求終止代理案件，亦有律師被約談及受到網絡攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n被關押在深圳鹽田看守所的12個香港人，據了解，他們的家屬早前已經分別找12個內地律師代理案件，其中3名近日收到警告，這宗案件不能接，向家屬提出要換人。<br />\n<br />\n早前去到看守所，申請會見的律師盧思位返回四川後，亦收到當地司法局的電話，要求他為代理這宗案件去備案，但他說對方並無要求他退出案件。盧思位律師：「就好了，我今天到司法局去，我覺得他們也沒說甚麼，就是說要求依法辦案，不要炒作，可能每一個地方司法局對這個案子認識不一樣，可能深圳司法局會覺得這個很敏感，可能這邊（四川）就覺得律師本身就是辦案子，依法辦案就好了。」<br />\n<br />\n相反，他在微博上受到更多網民的攻擊。盧思位：「有組織的，就有很多那種典型評論，跟我們這些律師扣了一些帽子，甚麼港獨、賣國賊、漢奸之類的。（有試過嗎？之前）沒有，我以前從來沒有，這種來攻擊過我，我也覺得很奇怪，而且我感覺這個一看就是有組織的。」<br />\n內地律師任全牛，星期一亦帶同家屬委託書申請會見當事人。據了解，當局再以「不能核實委託人身分」為理由，拒絕安排會面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=34938&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D34938%26ct%3D1&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=21754afb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=34938&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"45edc424fa71ddced339bbf8e0684b4e42e62f60","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5e28f671cb695e4b2df8df20d1d1082a071692","tid":2194681,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRespect<br />\n<br />\n剩低嗰啲"},{"pid":"a1a343c2fd251f65ae0153801cda438273249cb4","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"律師都唔接得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁最後仲有咩人可以見到佢哋"},{"pid":"e56d92d29de93be4d1031b852b214c6fbe98dc51","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07238d5e05fb9a93c38ebe4430254fcb700ad56","tid":2194681,"uid":269608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"陽光司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380b6ee588fb5da80c7cb8641fbc56e1b181faff","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d2ea254b881563fce02ecfb77345a67d60af36","tid":2194681,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43ab216d482e5178d89b49c9e6d6895887643561","tid":2194681,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"律師都唔俾見。痴撚線"},{"pid":"00934ef6aac8b643128971b8f2aca5346c474188","tid":2194681,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40e0a4c244c8c7d316ca553db5fa9bdbeb6c0dca","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf4787532aeb8705e024cad77a51e90e1c505ee","tid":2194681,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d264a44f02f0ffb76366bb4f4b391c6cd763d","tid":2194681,"uid":1